org.matrix.androidsdk.fragments

Class MatrixMessagesFragment

  • java.lang.Object
    • Fragment
      • org.matrix.androidsdk.fragments.MatrixMessagesFragment

  • public class MatrixMessagesFragment
extends Fragment
    A non-UI fragment containing logic for extracting messages from a room, including handling pagination. For a UI implementation of this, see MatrixMessageListFragment.
